Date: 2026-07-10

Description: IPCV - Scilab Image Processing and Computer Vision Toolbox.
 This release targets Scilab 2026.1 and OpenCV/OpenCV contrib 5.0.0.
 This revision adds classified test suites, machine-readable reports, and
 correctness contracts for image exchange, codecs, and native handles.
 
 OpenCV 5 and C++ Migration:
 - Target OpenCV/OpenCV contrib 5.0.0 for thirdparty builds.
 - Update gateway linking and C++ compile flags for OpenCV 5.
 - Provide Windows and Linux x64 native binaries for Scilab 2026.1.
 
 Main topics:
 - Camera and video handling.
 - Deep learning inference.
 - Feature detection, description, and matching.
 - Image arithmetic, filtering, enhancement, and restoration.
 - Morphological operations.
 - Object detection and tracking.
 - ROI processing and spatial transformations.
 - Structural analysis, image stitching, and super resolution.

